dct_description_sm: AMS 1 Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. Provisional G.S.G.S. no. 4379 (Middle East) United States. Army Map Service Great Britain. Army. Middle East Forces M.D.R. 539/8555 Alternte title: Taormina. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. Relief shown by contours at 10 metres interval (approx. only), and rock drawings. Electric power lines are located. "Drawn by 19th Fd. Survey Coy. R.E., June '43 from W.O. bromide. Printed by 514 C. Fd. Survey Coy, R.E. June, 43."
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
